# BOTOL #

web framework inspired by bottle (http://bottlepy.org)
written in PHP
---
uses external libraries such as : 
- Savant3 for templating
- RedBean for persistence
---
the simplest hello world in botol
```php
<?php
route('/hello/:name','hello');
function hello($arg)
{
    echo "hello,".$arg['name'];
}
```